settings.description: Climb up inside a volcano and go digging for Ace Coins!  Watch out, it's hot!
Use the metal mushroom to get to the top of the temple, where you'll face off against Big Boo!

Solve difficult puzzles while keeping Mario on his toes in this icy but warm ghost house.    

Hint: You can carry Flurries when above and on the side of it.
Use the power of dashing to get past the pesky tornadoes.
Mario's least threatening foes have come together to create insanity in the sewers.
Bullet Bills and Goombas' with shoes seem to want to ruin your day as you compete in the Green Mountain Climbing Contest.
Use the POW block to clear rows of enemies while solving puzzles in this watery ghost house.
I didn't actually create this level, a relative did.
To carry a flurry, press the run button when above it on a semisolid. Can be used in Freezeflame Manor.
Chargin' Chucks lead their fellow Bob-ombs into this tight, grassy water filled course.
Flutters fly across the sky and Wigglers are bound on ground in this simple nighttime course.
It's all just Tetriminos in this wacky world.

Ultra Star-esque Fast Parabeetle Platforming.
NOTE FOR SECTION 2: You can walk off a ledge and jump in midair with the kuribo's shoe.
In this field, Fireflowers grow naturally out of the floor, how convenient!
Galoombas walk around in their peaceful hills, with lots of sandy and thin structures.
